{"id": 58369, "date": "2025-08-12T04:00:27", "date_gmt": "2025-08-12T11:00:27", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=58369"}, "modified": "2025-08-09T11:10:13", "modified_gmt": "2025-08-09T18:10:13", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-august-12-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/08/12/kingdom-of-days-august-12-2/", "title": {"rendered": "Kingdom of Days: August 12"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><em><strong>New for 2025:\u00a0</strong>New entry for 1977</em></p>\n<p><strong>1967:\u00a0</strong>The Castiles play the Surf &#8216;N&#8217;See Club in Sea Bright, New Jersey. That night, Bruce and some of his bandmates catch The Blues Magoos and The Who opening for Herman&#8217;s Hermits at Convention Hall in Asbury Park. Just a few weeks later, the band will cover The Blues Magoos&#8217; &#8220;<a href=\"http://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2020/07/28/cover-me-one-by-one/\">One By One</a>&#8221; in concert themselves.</p>\n<p><strong>1972:\u00a0</strong>Bruce plays his fourth of six\u00a0two-shows-a-night solo gigs at Max&#8217;s Kansas City that week.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"11977\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1972-08-11-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/1972-08-11-1.jpg?fit=500%2C319&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"500,319\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1972-08-11\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/1972-08-11-1.jpg?fit=300%2C191&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/1972-08-11-1.jpg?fit=500%2C319&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-11977\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/1972-08-11-1-300x191.jpg?resize=758%2C483\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"483\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/1972-08-11-1.jpg?resize=300%2C191&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/1972-08-11-1.jpg?w=500&amp;ssl=1 500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1974</strong>:\u00a0Bruce cancels a gig at the Cambridge Performance Center to make room for <em>Born to Run\u00a0</em>recording sessions.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"11965\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1974-08-11/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/1974-08-11.jpg?fit=290%2C500&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"290,500\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1974-08-11\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/1974-08-11.jpg?fit=174%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/1974-08-11.jpg?fit=290%2C500&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-11965\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/1974-08-11-174x300.jpg?resize=758%2C1308\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1308\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/1974-08-11.jpg?resize=174%2C300&amp;ssl=1 174w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/1974-08-11.jpg?w=290&amp;ssl=1 290w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1975:\u00a0</strong>Columbia Records begins distributing a limited run of advanced promo copies of\u00a0<em>Born to Run.</em></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"3846\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1975-0812/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1975-0812.jpg?fit=872%2C631&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"872,631\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1975-0812\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1975-0812.jpg?fit=300%2C217&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1975-0812.jpg?fit=758%2C549&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3846\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1975-0812-300x217.jpg?resize=758%2C549\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"549\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1975-0812.jpg?resize=300%2C217&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1975-0812.jpg?resize=768%2C556&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1975-0812.jpg?w=872&amp;ssl=1 872w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1977:\u00a0</strong>At Atlantic Studios in New York City, Bruce and the E Street Band record &#8220;<a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2021/02/08/roll-of-the-dice-gotta-get-that-feeling/\">Gotta Get That Feeling.</a>&#8221; It will be released 38 years later.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Bruce Springsteen Get that Feeling\" width=\"758\" height=\"569\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/DQ1LfLDrDrU?list=PLp97J3OSn7Isbkt20--RCkDWLCYDDJ3wX\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<p><strong>1978:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band bring the Darkness Tour to Augusta, Maine, for one show at the Civic Center.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"3670\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1978-0812/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1978-0812.jpg?fit=666%2C885&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"666,885\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1978-0812\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1978-0812.jpg?fit=226%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1978-0812.jpg?fit=666%2C885&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3670\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1978-0812-226x300.jpg?resize=758%2C1006\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1006\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1978-0812.jpg?resize=226%2C300&amp;ssl=1 226w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1978-0812.jpg?w=666&amp;ssl=1 666w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1981:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band play their second of two nights at Detroit&#8217;s Joe Louis Arena on the original River Tour. Mitch Ryder makes a guest appearance during the encores on (what else?) &#8220;<a href=\"http://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2019/12/27/cover-me-detroit-medley/\">Detroit Medley.</a>&#8221;</p>\n<div id=\"v-O8YUTq5R-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/O8YUTq5R?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Detroit 12/08/1981\" width=\"758\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLJTyL9twk3zA1TFgf6jVO6s3jMFbLoHkt\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<p><strong>1984:\u00a0</strong>Southside Johnny guest-stars on &#8220;Twist and Shout&#8221; at Night Six of a ten-night Meadowlands stand on the Born in the U.S.A. Tour.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Bruce Springsteen Born In The USA , New Jersey 1984\" width=\"758\" height=\"569\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/xQWHgkEPO6M?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Bruce Springsteen &quot;Out in the Street&quot; 1984\" width=\"758\" height=\"569\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ltFmBMtLr3A?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<p><strong>1998:\u00a0</strong>Bruce takes in a Yankees game and stops by the clubhouse to sign a guitar.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Bruce Springsteen catches a Yankees game - August 12, 1998\" width=\"758\" height=\"569\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/59rOfptTacI?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20311\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1998-08-11a/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1998-08-11a.png?fit=1326%2C871&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1326,871\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1998-08-11a\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1998-08-11a.png?fit=300%2C197&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1998-08-11a.png?fit=758%2C498&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20311\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1998-08-11a-300x197.png?resize=758%2C497\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"497\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1998-08-11a.png?resize=300%2C197&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1998-08-11a.png?resize=1024%2C673&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1998-08-11a.png?resize=768%2C504&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1998-08-11a.png?w=1326&amp;ssl=1 1326w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20312\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1998-08-11b/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1998-08-11b.png?fit=1373%2C1399&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1373,1399\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1998-08-11b\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1998-08-11b.png?fit=294%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1998-08-11b.png?fit=758%2C772&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20312\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1998-08-11b-294x300.png?resize=758%2C774\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"774\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1998-08-11b.png?resize=294%2C300&amp;ssl=1 294w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1998-08-11b.png?resize=768%2C783&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1998-08-11b.png?resize=50%2C50&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1999:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band wrap up their astounding fifteen-night Reunion stand at the Meadowlands with two long-awaited and inevitable bookends: the show-opening tour premiere of &#8220;<a href=\"http://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2019/07/24/cover-me-roll-of-the-dice-jersey-girl/\">Jersey Girl</a>&#8221; and the show-closing one-off performance of &#8220;Rosalita (Come Out Tonight).&#8221; During the encores, Jon Bon Jovi, Richie Sambora, and Melissa Etheridge join Bruce and the band for &#8220;<a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2022/12/21/roll-of-the-dice-hungry-heart/\">Hungry Heart</a>.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Bruce Springsteen Jersey Girl (Live 1999 08 12)\" width=\"758\" height=\"569\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/DNzLnlxJh20?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Bruce Springsteen with JBJ And Richie  Hungry Heart\" width=\"758\" height=\"569\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/tp5QXKa6DIU?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<div id=\"v-kGzGDIv0-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='568' src='https://videopress.com/embed/kGzGDIv0?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20313\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1999-08-12/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1999-08-12.png?fit=1144%2C1404&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1144,1404\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1999-08-12\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1999-08-12.png?fit=244%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-fi